flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|strength_1|1|Adapting to the task|You can change how you approach work depending on what it needs. This helps when one fixed routine would be too narrow.|deep_focus|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::strength_1
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|strength_2|2|Using more than one route|You may be able to move between focus, ideas, movement, and conversation without treating any one condition as the only answer.|creative_movement|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::strength_2
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|strength_3|3|Reading your state|You can often notice when the work needs a shift in pace, setting, attention, or input. This gives you more ways to recover progress.|physical_rhythm|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::strength_3
12_Narrowing
domain_key|pattern_key|narrowing_key|priority|narrowing_title|narrowing_text|missing_range_signal_key|status|lookup_key
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|narrowing_1|1|Switching too soon|You may change conditions before the work has had enough time to develop. A different route can feel useful, even when the real need is to stay with the current one a little longer.|deep_focus|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::narrowing_1
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|narrowing_2|2|Mistaking flexibility for progress|Trying a new angle, moving around, or talking something through can feel productive. The risk is using variety when the work now needs a choice.|creative_movement|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::narrowing_2
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|narrowing_3|3|Leaving feedback until later|Because several routes are available, you may try to solve the work through your own process first. A timely outside response can stop you spending too long choosing alone.|social_exchange|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::narrowing_3
13_Application
domain_key|pattern_key|application_area|guidance_type|priority|guidance_text|linked_signal_key|status|lookup_key
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|use_this_when|guidance|1|Use this pattern when the work could start in more than one way. Before you begin, name the condition the task most needs: quiet focus, a fresh angle, movement, or a useful conversation.|deep_focus|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::use_this_when
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|watch_for|guidance|2|Watch for the moment when changing conditions becomes a way to avoid deciding. If the work is already moving, stay with it long enough to see what it produces.|creative_movement|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::watch_for
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|develop_by|guidance|3|Develop by choosing one route for the first stretch of work. Set a simple checkpoint, then decide whether to stay focused, move, open ideas, or ask for input.|social_exchange|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::develop_by
14_Closing_Integration
domain_key|pattern_key|score_shape|closing_summary|core_gift|core_trap|development_edge|memorable_line|status|lookup_key
flow_state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|balanced|This result points to a flexible flow profile. Deep Focus is the first signal to check, but Creative Movement, Physical Rhythm, and Social Exchange are all close enough to matter. You are likely to work best when you choose the condition that fits the task, then give it enough time to work.|Your gift is the ability to adapt your route into flow without being locked into one method.|The trap is changing conditions before the work has enough direction or depth.|The useful edge is to choose the route the work needs now, then review it at a clear checkpoint.|Choose the condition. Give it time. Then adjust with purpose.|active|flow_state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::balanced
